HEADWORD: Dominion Day
<hw>Do*min"ion Day</hw>. <def>In Canada, a legal holiday, July lst,
being the anniversary of the proclamation of the formation of the
Dominion in 1867.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

